#~ msgid ""
#~ "A Ghostscript version that is maintained by Easy Software Products. It "
#~ "includes pre-compiled Gimp-Print drivers for many inkjets (plus some "
#~ "other goodies). ESP Ghostscript will produce photographic quality prints "
#~ "in many cases, especially with the Epson Stylus model series. ESP "
#~ "Ghostscript is GPL-software."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ghostscripti versioon, mida hooldab firma Easy Software Products. See "
#~ "sisaldab eelkompileeritud Gimp-Printi juhtprogramme paljudele "
#~ "tindiprinteritele ja veel terve hulga häid asju. ESP Ghostscript suudab "
#~ "paljudel juhtudel pakkuda fotokvaliteediga trükki, eriti just Epsoni "
#~ "Stylus seeria printeritel. ESP Ghostscript on GPL litsentsiga vabavara."

